  <!-- EN: mechanoid egg -->
  <GR_ElectroEgg.label>机械蛋</GR_ElectroEgg.label>
  <!-- EN: This diminutive egg seems to be metallic in nature at first, yet it is soft enough to crush it between two fingers. Once thus crushed it can be swallowed normally, and the active mechanites inside have a reinvigorating effect on the consumer. This effect can be slightly addictive, though. -->
  <GR_ElectroEgg.description>小巧精致的机械蛋。虽然外壳似乎生来就是金属制的，但却软到用两根手指就能捏碎。你可以像喝饮料一样享用蛋内的液体，里面含有的活化型纳米机械则具有振奋精神的作用。过于频繁享用可能会导致上瘾。</GR_ElectroEgg.description>
